{"tid":1467164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[注意]希望各位拎住美國旗嘅時候 唔好亂咁做野","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:28:57.000Z","uid":9564,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1086ac78799529736fac3a6730f86feeaf23ce0a","tid":1467164,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"拎住支美國旗沖去阻住救護員 比美國人見到人哋會有咩感覺？<br />\n有時冷靜少少 諗下應唔應該做先<br />\n我哋仲要等美國國會九月復會 呢段時間唔好令到美國人難做好冇？"},{"pid":"faf322d81b55282d8577740741f68a80332af768","tid":1467164,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90b50d20995fffd510e5df9fdb74b63ce4bd9234","tid":1467164,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e49ff01bcc3cff62ed5dd68e539109ba37f24da8","tid":1467164,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09d067e0ef0c7c8fc4719e76a273b41271bafd48","tid":1467164,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過去嘅事 已經過左去 請著力宣傳818百萬大遊行及防暴警向機場拔槍</span></span>"},{"pid":"97605ee4ee44bb6628a6bc333cdb865cfcb34515","tid":1467164,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得道歉會顯出我們大方<br />\n<br />\n今日有兩個重要信息 <br />\n一係要拆鬼呢招 對家玩spy防不勝防 要想辦法破狗狗情報網/截取狗狗情報<br />\n二係前線手足呢兩個月壓力好大 情緒控制唔好 可能要休養下 和理非要出場<br />\n<br />\n其實今日好小事 與721 811相比 雞毛蒜皮<br />\n文宣 要拆今日單野 盡量冷處理"},{"pid":"1d95245433d4ea612a9848c570ba6280733387c3","tid":1467164,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩有位手足就係咁 好彩有人捉住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bff75c62cbe1217450d180c8691788062188f5c","tid":1467164,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d067e0ef0c7c8fc4719e76